<video autoplay muted loop id="myVideo">
<source src=<%= asset_path('bg.mp4') %> type=video/mp4>
</video>

<div class="column">
  <div class="CTA-box col-sm-12 col-md-6">
    <img src=<%= asset_path('lama.png') %>>
    <div class="heading">
      <h1>The only secret santa tool you'll ever need.</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="CTA">
    <%= link_to 'Create a group', new_group_path, class: 'btn btn-secondary btn-l' %>

    <% if user_signed_in? == false %>
    <p class="login-cta"><%= link_to 'Or log in to view your group', user_session_path %></p>
    </div>
    <% end %>

    <div class="home-action">
    <% if user_signed_in? && current_user.group_id != nil %>
      <%= link_to 'Go to my group', group_path(current_user.group_id), class: 'btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm' %>
    <% end %>

    <% if user_signed_in? %>
      <%= link_to 'logout', destroy_user_session_path, :method => :delete, class: 'btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm' %>
    <% end %>
    </div>

    <!-- Button trigger modal -->
    <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-secondary" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#exampleModal" style="margin-top: 30px;">
      What the fork is secret santa?
    </button>

    <!-- Modal -->
    <div class="modal fade" id="exampleModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="exampleModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
        <div class="modal-content">
          <div class="modal-header">
            <h5 class="modal-title" id="exampleModalLabel">Holy moly. What a tool ðŸŽ…</h5>
            <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
              <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
            </button>
          </div>
          <div class="modal-body">
            <h3>About this tool</h3>
            Holy moly allows you to create a group, invite your peers with a unique link and conduct a secret drawing.</br>
            Once the group admin conducts the drawing, every participant sees whom he/she has to give a gift to.</br>
            At the moment, you can only be part of one group with one e-mail address.</br></br>
            Currently, the e-mail function does not work yet. So once the group is drawn, all participants have to check back to the group link in order to see whom she/he has to give a gift to.</br></br>

            <h3>About secret santa</h3>
            Secret santa is a game, usually played during the christmas time amongst friends, family or colleagues.
            The concept is quite simple. Every participant secretly draws a name of another participant.
            The secret santa (the giver) then needs to give one or multiple gifts to his/her receiver.
            Depending on the group, you can define own rules (number of gifts, value per gift, etc.).
          </div>
          <div class="modal-footer">
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-secondary" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
            <%= link_to 'Create a group', new_group_path, class: 'btn btn-secondary btn-l' %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>


  </div>
</div>
